<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Verify your email</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f6f8fb; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; }
    .wrapper { width: 100%; padding: 24px 0; }
    .card { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); overflow: hidden; }
    .header { background: #0b72ff; color: #fff; padding: 20px 28px; }
    .brand { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.3px; }
    .content { padding: 28px; color: #1f2937; }
    .title { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #111827; }
    .subtitle { margin: 0 0 18px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 15px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #0b72ff; color: #fff; padding: 12px 18px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
    .link { word-break: break-all; color: #0b72ff; text-decoration: none; }
    .code { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 6px; text-align: center; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 8px; background: #f1f5f9; color: #0b72ff; margin: 10px 0 18px; }
    .note { font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; }
    .divider { height: 1px; background: #e5e7eb; margin: 24px 0; }
    .footer { padding: 18px 28px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; background: #f9fafb; }
    .footer a { color: #0b72ff; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
  <!--[if mso]>
    <style>
      .button { font-family: Arial, sans-serif !important; }
    </style>
  <![endif]-->
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="brand">Personal Wings</div>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h1 class="title">Verify your email</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Thanks for creating an account. Please confirm your email to activate your profile.</p>

        <p style="text-align:center; margin: 16px 0 18px;">
          <a class="button" href="{{verificationUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Verify Email</a>
        </p>

        <p class="note">If the button doesn’t work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
        <p><a class="link" href="{{verificationUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{verificationUrl}}</a></p>

        {{#if verificationCode}}
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <p class="subtitle">Or enter this 6‑digit code:</p>
          <div class="code">{{verificationCode}}</div>
        {{/if}}

        <p class="note">This verification link expires in 24 hours.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>If you didn’t create a Personal Wings account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
